        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "I've tested dozens of PDF tools over the years, and Foxit PDF consistently stands out for how it combines professional power with everyday simplicity. Whether you're a freelancer handling contracts or part of a large team collaborating on reports, Foxit PDF adapts to your needs without the steep learning curve.",
            "marks": []
