      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Foxit PDF is designed for people who actually work with PDFs daily, not just view them. The interface feels familiar if you've used office software, so you won't waste time hunting for tools. What I appreciate most is how it balances advanced features with accessibility—you can start with basic editing and gradually explore more sophisticated options as your needs grow.",
