          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The AI integration is particularly smart. Instead of being a gimmick, it actually helps with tasks like summarizing long documents, extracting key data, and even suggesting edits. It's the kind of tool that grows with you.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
